snippet.title: Galactigun Ft. DJ Kranius - Moving Mountains
snippet.description: The eccentric alien, DJ Kranius, has attacked our galaxy with epic beats of bass dropping proportions. You must save the universe from his mesmerizing audio armada. Travel through the synthwave torrent, destroying enemy ships to the beat. Use precise timing to accelerate your score and earn credits.
